          "reviewBody": "Teachers behaved badly to the little children thinking that they werent being watched. After reporting to principal rohini she covered up the whole issue. The teachers are not qualified and they are very partial to celebrity kids and those who are rich, they dont treat everyone equally. Not a place for value education and learning. Worst attitude of mrs. Rohini. Very few good teachers are good but they too get spoiled by the show off attitude unfortunately. Good infrastructure and efforts by most parents for their kids growth are positives.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
